reviews.author: Angela Pensiero
reviews.text: I ordered chicken with vegetables and shrimp fried rice on Grubhub. The chicken and vegetables came in a white gooey disgusting sauce with overcooked chicken. I could not eat it. It was not edible. I called the restaurant and they put me through to the manager twice she did not respond left her a voicemail then I tried to call back third time and they blocked me. I will never order from here again.

reviews.author: Ankita Ajjampur
reviews.text: Good Chinese carry out!! Dinner special was a good deal and they use fresh vegetables in their food

reviews.author: ANIYAH DUBUISSON
reviews.text: if i could leave a 0 STAR review i would. my boyfriend ordered our food from here and im highly disappointed. i got white rice w a side of shrimp and broccoli. i took about 2 bites and noticed a piece of hair on the fork and in my rice. i’m upset that we spent damn near $40 in total on both of our meals in exchange for these people not even being the slightest bit of sanitary. please do not order from here. this place is disgusting .

reviews.author: CareBear
reviews.text: First time was disappointed. Tasted the chicken and broccoli this time and it tasted like solely corn Starch . I couldn't taste anything else but massive corn Strach it was sooo thick much more than usual. Usually it's a light sauce. Was disappointed because I ordered for a large group who felt the same about their dishes who has never eaten here before.

reviews.author: Aaron Hammer
reviews.text: The perfect local Chinese’s food. Not much more to add
